Please download the current oscap files to this directory using:

wget http://www.redhat.com/security/data/oval/com.redhat.rhsa-all.xml
wget http://www.redhat.com/security/data/metrics/com.redhat.rhsa-all.xccdf.xml

After downloading the the files, the big one need to be compressed to reduce the
Puppet transfer size:

bzip2 com.redhat.rhsa-all.xml
